Title name:

Life Sciences Research Paper Abstract Summarizer

Problem Statement:

Researchers in life sciences need quick summaries of lengthy research papers to stay updated, but reading full papers is time-consuming.

Steps:

Use a Large Language Model to process research paper abstracts or full texts.

Develop an Al agent that generates concise summaries highlighting key findings.

Format summaries for easy reading and sharing.

Support batch processing of multiple papers.

Data Requirements:

Research paper abstracts or full texts from open-access life sciences journals in text format.

Expected Output:

Concise, structured summaries of research papers in text format.
